{
  "stem": "935.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "In all the time I was there, I was looking for exit-- there was no exit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "There was only entrance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't find out where Auschwitz was, or that we were in Auschwitz, until the next day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until the very next day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not that it meant anything to me at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I just know it was the end of the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was in a country which was no country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were no trees, there was no sky, there was no heaven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only a sun, which burnt-- which burned you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Cold at night, freezing cold at night, because it's kind of a desert climate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And something which does not belong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not that it doesn't belong, but it doesn't belong to this Earth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is absolutely-- I don't know where they found that place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yes, I had heard, much, much later, that the place where they built Auschwitz on-- or Birkenau-- was originally, way back when, a battleground where Russian and, I don't know, somebody else, fought another war.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that these-- these barracks-- or stables, which they called our quarters-- had been stables for the horses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That on this earth, where we were walking on, underneath were a lot of buried Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That this was a battleground once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were first-- I think they do this on purpose, really, to introduce you very quickly to-- that this is-- that hell is heaven compared to that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, again, those typical [NON-ENGLISH] bureaus, where little girls sit with pretty dresses and clean faces and hair and so on, and ask name and address, and all this kind of thing, from one to the other?",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
